description:
Join Sarah Wright, Eric Christian Olsen, Anna, and Sim as they talk to two callers…

…Jennifer, 39, is calling from Massachusetts to talk about co-parenting with her narcissistic ex-husband, who won’t allow Jennifer to meet his new girlfriend, a woman that is spending a lot of time with Jennifer’s daughter. Can the Unqualified team help Jennifer solve this co-parenting power struggle?

…Kindra, 27, is calling from Edmonton, Canada to discuss a flirtatious new relationship that’s been developing between Kindra and her husband and a couple that they recently met at a wedding. After learning that this couple is in an open relationship, Kindra needs help figuring out whether her and her husband should invite this couple into their bedroom…
